Dialogue: 1,0:21:03.41,0:21:05.87,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(603,15)\fad(300,300)}So I pray
Dialogue: 1,0:21:05.57,0:21:09.46,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(603,15)\fad(300,300)}But you're fading away
Dialogue: 1,0:21:10.52,0:21:16.63,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(603,15)\fad(300,300)}Don't go and break my fragile heart
