Dialogue: 1,0:21:33.74,0:21:37.48,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(603,15)\fad(300,300)}Calling you, so like a little child
Dialogue: 1,0:21:37.44,0:21:40.75,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(603,15)\fad(300,300)}All the things you have in mind
Dialogue: 1,0:21:40.77,0:21:44.16,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(603,15)\fad(300,300)}I wish I could say your insides
